454
00:17:42,680 --> 00:17:43,460
Cháu ngoại nhỏ.

455
00:17:43,460 --> 00:17:43,960
Đẹp trai thế.

456
00:17:43,960 --> 00:17:44,600
Cháu ngoại nhỏ.

457
00:17:45,200 --> 00:17:46,360
Cô bé xinh đẹp đằng sau

458
00:17:46,520 --> 00:17:47,600
