00:31:38,290 --> 00:31:39,180
Cháu rót cho chú cốc nước nhé.

785
00:31:39,180 --> 00:31:39,730
Chú phấn khích.

786
00:31:39,730 --> 00:31:40,420
Không sao.

787
00:31:40,440 --> 00:31:41,080
Cháu cứ gói đi.

788
00:31:41,800 --> 00:31:42,720
